path.desc: This is a description of district-n1. In other words, the res-nat quarantine zone where nat administers periodic whipping to res for no particular reasons other than the feelgood factor. Occassionally, the sounds of keyboard clicks could be heard from neighboring districts. Some Alenxandrians theorize that it must be the result of nat taping keyboards to res' fingers in order to make him write F/SN lore.;https://cdn.discordapp.com/emojis/918035156537864214.webp

path.desc: This is a description of district-n2. This is the brainworm factory, or, as some have come to call it the horny corner. It is a most despicable corner of Alexandria filled with the unadulterated brain juices of those who always let their thoughts run ahead of their keyboards and rack up dozens upon dozens of sheet/thread debt. Alas, Alexandria does not have an adequate sewage system to contain this brand of filth in particular.;https://cdn.discordapp.com/emojis/764198114356625439.webp
